title: President commences “Pibidemu Polonnaruwa” (The President of the Democratic Socialist Republic of Sri Lanka)
text: ( Source : The President of the Democratic Socialist Republic of Sri Lanka ) 'Pibidemu Polonnaruwa ( Awakening of Polonnaruwa)' District Development Project was commenced today ( Oct. 17 ), under the patronage of President Maithripala Sirisena .
